    	<div1>
    		<div2>
    			<div3 type="in-memoriam">
    				<head>
    					<title type="main">Allen Ginsberg<lb/>
    			1926-1997</title>
    				</head>
    			</div3>
    			<p>“He was asked recently to define himself. He replied, ‘Oh, that’s easy. Beat writer, Blake
scholar, <corr type="emend">Buddhist</corr> harmonium-player, Jewish
punk rocker, once dangerous subversive. Or maybe just poet.’”</p>
				<p><hi rend="i">The Sunday Times</hi>, 6 April 1997</p>
